title: Owusu’s catch, McCaffrey’s 243 yards highlight Stanford win
text:
Photo: Thearon W. Henderson, Getty Images Francis Owusu #6 of the Stanford Cardinal's catches a touchdown pass up against the back of Jaleel Wadood #2 of the UCLA Bruins in the third quarter of an NCAA football game at Stanford Stadium on October 15, 2015 in Stanford, California.
Francis Owusu #6 of the Stanford Cardinal's catches a touchdown...
In another display of offensive fireworks for Stanford on Thursday night, Christian McCaffrey staged a Heisman-caliber performance.
